{"tid":1329112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(告黑警)委國示威少年臉中52橡膠彈致失明　兩警被控企圖謀殺","createTime":"2019-07-18T06:12:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T14:45:59.000Z","uid":235152,"like":443,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"e2710c05e7f124fa289e21a3ecbac303338c9463","tid":1329112,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:12:04.000Z","msg":"一名委內瑞拉16歲少年查孔（Rufo Chacon）在當地的示威活動中，臉部被警方發射52顆橡膠子彈而導致失明，其中16顆橡膠子彈更直接射向其雙眼。事後委內瑞拉當局公布，兩名警員被控對示威者「企圖謀殺，不當使用武器和殘酷對待」， <br />\n<br />\n當地警方的調查報告稱，國家安全部隊在沒有任何警告下強行鎮壓民眾。聯合國人權事務高級專員Michelle Bachelet發表報告，譴責委內瑞拉侵犯人權。"},{"pid":"c2e7070f3ca6b4e24be82e5fee67fafc096d7b23","tid":1329112,"uid":21545,"like":198,"dislike":0,"score":198,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:12:40.000Z","msg":"52粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004abd8c99ea33aa1d7a396e89c32d69ff8fc09a","tid":1329112,"uid":94834,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:13:12.000Z","msg":"連發？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006a74eda046068cece3406b81601c0ee722246d","tid":1329112,"uid":235152,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"c2e7070f3ca6b4e24be82e5fee67fafc096d7b23","tid":1329112,"uid":21545,"like":198,"dislike":0,"score":198,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:12:40.000Z","msg":"52粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:13:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20